    <string name="god_father_explanation">Each night, you select a player to eliminate. Your decision has higher priority than other Mafia members.</string>
    <string name="saul_goodman_explanation">If a Mafia dies, you can take their place. Once, you may convert a simple citizen into a Mafia member.</string>
    <string name="mafia_explanation">Each night, you vote with fellow Mafia members to select one player to eliminate.</string>
    <string name="doctor_explanation">Each night, you can protect one player from death. You cannot choose the same player two nights in a row.</string>
    <string name="surgeon_explanation">You are part of the Mafia. Each night, you can save one player from death. You may choose yourself.</string>
    <string name="detective_explanation">Each night, you investigate one player to determine whether they are a member of the Mafia.</string>
    <string name="civilian_explanation">You have no night action. During the day, you must observe carefully and vote wisely.</string>
    <string name="sniper_explanation">During the game nights, you can shoot two times. If the target is Mafia, they die. Otherwise, you die instead.</string>
    <string name="silencer_explanation">You can silence a player on two separate nights during the game. The silenced player cannot speak the next day.</string>
    <string name="bomber_explanation">If you die, two players next to you also die.</string>
    <string name="bulletproof_explanation">You are immune to the first night-time attack. After that, you become vulnerable like others.</string>
    <string name="mayor_explanation">You have no night action, but you know the Doctor and Surgeon roles. The game master informs you about them.</string>
    <string name="nostradamus_explanation">At the introduction night, you choose three players, and the game master tells you how many of them are Mafia. The Godfather is not counted as Mafia.</string>
    <string name="joker_explanation">You have no night action. Your goal is to get voted out during the day in order to win the game.</string>
    <string name="gunsmith_explanation">Each night gives two players a gun. Guns may be blanks or real and can be fired once during the day.</string>
    <string name="ranger_explanation">If targeted by Mafia, can shoot. Stays alive if hitting Mafia, dies if hitting Civilian.</string>


